title: Barbarian w3 late game
comment_one:
*1= Boost your wis if need accuracy

comment_two: After maxing dmg talents you want to go for hp talents, to boost "Meatshank" bonus
comment_three: Max "Apocalypse Zow", "Back to Basics" and "No Pain No Gain" then put points into other active skills.
notes: At this level you should be able to tell which talent will benefit you the most, as some might be situational.
